snippet.title: Banks Will Serve Their Customers Only Today; Senior Citizens Exempted

localized.description:
Banks will attend their customers only today. Senior citizens exempted have been exempted. Since last ten days banks were unable to do their routine works and were busy in exchanging currency notes of Rs 500 and Rs 1000
